    "text": "To see that n divides an, factor n as 2km, with m odd. Then note that k In _n(n - 1)/2, and that there exists i≤m - 1 such that m divides 2' - 1, namely i = Ф(m) (Euler's totient function: the number of integers in {1,..., m} relatively prime to m).",
