    "text": "Now if P(x) = [\"_oaja, then the relation P(x) = Cx7p\" (x) implies that aj = Cj(j- 1)aj for all j; hence aj=0 for j {n - 1, and we conclude that P(x) = Anx\", which has all identical roots.",
